	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/paths.pdb
	* tools/pdbgen/pdb/paint_tools.pdb: pass the error to the stroke
	functions.

	* app/pdb/paint_tools_cmds.c
	* app/pdb/edit_cmds.c
	* app/pdb/paths_cmds.c: regenerated.

