2007-11-26  Sven Neumann  <sven@gimp.org>

	* plug-ins/common/wmf.c: avoid filename encoding problems by not
	using wmf_file_open() but mapping the file into memory with
	GMappedFile. Fixes bug #499329.

2007-11-26  Sven Neumann  <sven@gimp.org>

